cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use VSBS in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "VSBS: Autonomous Vehicle Service Booking System"
abstract: >-
  VSBS is a zero-touch, safety-first, research-cited autonomous vehicle
  service booking system. It composes a LangGraph supervisor, a provider-
  agnostic LLM layer, a deterministic sensor simulator with Kalman fusion,
  a prognostic health state machine aligned to ISO 13374 and ISO 21448,
  and a DPDP-native consent log into an end-to-end autonomous service
  advisor. Every architectural decision is traceable to peer-reviewed
  research or published standards, and the project ships with a
  defensive publication establishing prior art for twelve inventive
  concepts.
type: software
